## Part C — Create Release v0.1.0 with CPack artifacts (most important)

This is the “Build Tools” finishing move.

### Step 1: Build and create packages locally
On your Xubuntu terminal:

```bash
cd /media/waqasm86/External1/Project-CPP/Project-Qt/cmake-superbuild-toolkit

rm -rf build
cmake -S . -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DMYAPP_ENABLE_PACKAGING=ON
cmake --build build

# Create the CPack packages
cpack --config build/CPackConfig.cmake
